                    PAYROLL CALCULATION GUIDE (2026 RATES)
================================================================================

DEDUCTION FORMULAS:
-------------------
| Deduction   | Formula                                      |
|-------------|----------------------------------------------|
| SSS         | Base × 4.5%                                  |
