================================================================================
                         SAMPLE CALCULATION
================================================================================

GIVEN:
  Salary 15th:    PHP 30,000.00
  Salary 30th:    PHP 30,000.00
  Overtime Hours: 5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
EARNINGS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Base monthly
  1000 + 1000 = 2000

Total work hours/month
  22 × 8 = 176

Hourly rate
  2000 ÷ 176 = 11.363636...

Overtime pay
  11.363636... × 3 × 1.10 = 37.50

Bonus (15%)
  2000 × 0.15 = 300.00

Gross earnings
  2000 + 37.50 + 300.00 = 2337.50

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEDUCTIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SSS (4.5%)
  2000 × 0.045 = 90.00

PhilHealth (2.5%)
  2000 × 0.025 = 50.00

Pag-IBIG (2%)
  2000 × 0.02 = 40.00

Taxable income (for tax computation)
  2337.50 - 90 - 50 - 40 = 2157.50

Income Tax (2026, max 30% - Monthly)
  Monthly taxable = 2157.50
  Since 2157.50 < 20,833 → 0% bracket
  Income tax = PHP 0.00

Total deductions
  90 + 50 + 40 + 0 = 180.00

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NET PAY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Net pay
  2337.50 - 180.00 = 2157.50

================================================================================
                           FINAL ANSWERS
================================================================================

  Overtime         = PHP     37.50
  Bonus            = PHP    300.00
  Gross            = PHP  2,337.50
  Income Tax       = PHP      0.00
  Total Deductions = PHP    180.00
  Net Pay          = PHP  2,157.50

